  "detailed_description": "You are in a Maze. You need to get out of it. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game all in all has ONLY 12 Levels generated randomly.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo do this, you will sometimes need blue diamonds, and you can exchange green ones for useful features to get out of the Maze.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse button 'B' button to exchange green diamonds.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse button 'K' button to mark territory.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse button 'L' button to use Navigator.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse button 'P' button to use Scanner.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can use the Navigator, Thread Of Ariadne, and Scanner in the game to get out.",
